article_id:2489,category_name:News,title_name:The 3rd Anniversary Dragalia Digest and Special Website Are Now Available! [Update],image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/fa6c57899a29e7bf0d2d50d4a43fbb4f.png,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1632807000"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>In the Dragalia Digest video that went live on 9/24, Notte says that &quot;all Gala adventurers will have their appearance rates boosted&quot; in the Gala Dragalia summon showcase mentioned around the 2:45 mark. In fact, only certain Gala adventurers and dragons have boosted appearance rates.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>The latest episode of Dragalia Digest, streamed on YouTube around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1632452400"></span>, is now available to watch as a video on the official Nintendo Mobile YouTube channel.</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/fa6c57899a29e7bf0d2d50d4a43fbb4f.png"></div><div><br></div><div>This episode features information on some of the events and new features that are coming to the game as part of the 3rd Anniversary update.</div><div><br></div><div>▼Video URL</div><div><a href="https://youtu.be/eTWpna9jt2U">https://youtu.be/eTWpna9jt2U</a></div><div><br></div><div>There&#39;s also a special website that includes the information covered in the video.</div><div><br></div><div>▼Special website</div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/3rd_anniv/">https://dragalialost.com/en/3rd_anniv/</a></div><div><br></div><div>What&#39;s more, we will send all players the following gifts to commemorate the release of this very special episode!</div><div><br></div><div>■Gifts</div><div>・Tenfold Summon Voucher &times; 1</div><div>・Rupie &times; 100,000,000</div><div><br></div><div>Note: The gifts can be claimed from your goodie box for up to seven days after logging in. If the gifts aren&#39;t retrieved within seven days, they will be lost.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1632454200,update_time1632807910